  • Method Details

    • interpolate

      T interpolate(List<String> fragments, BiStream<Substring.Match, Object> placeholders)
      Interpolates with fragments of size N + 1 and placeholders of size N. The placeholders BiStream includes pairs of placeholder names in the form of "{foo}" and their corresponding values passed through the varargs parameter of StringFormat.Template.with(java.lang.Object...).
